The paper focuses on the development of a tool for expressing and verifying requirements for control systems, which involves software engineering (cs.SE), programming languages (cs.PL), logic (cs.LO), and system design (cs.SY). Additionally, the use of AutoReq involves automated reasoning and decision-making, which could fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
